{"tw": {"4257850": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "妖狐的深夜特訓 未來篇", "steam_appid": 4257850, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/38197db26d84d22c082e32a1d9522158.poster.avif?t=1776304865\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/38197db26d84d22c082e32a1d9522158.webm?t=1776304865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/38197db26d84d22c082e32a1d9522158.mp4?t=1776304865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[妖狐的深夜特訓 未來篇]是[妖狐的深夜直播]的後日談故事。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[妖狐的深夜特訓 未來篇]為獨立作品，遊玩[妖狐的深夜特訓 未來篇]不需要擁有[妖狐的深夜直播]，但我們建議先遊玩，這樣[妖狐的深夜特訓 未來篇]才能有更佳的劇情體驗。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著朝夕相處，他漸漸看見她純真而善良的本質，遠非世人所言的邪惡之物。愛意悄然萌芽，兩人攜手面對誤解與挑戰，並肩阻止了世界的崩壞，擊退了誓言獵殺妖狐的神獸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，在穿越無數世界線、終於抵達完美結局之後，驅魔師的身心卻因精氣耗盡而逐漸衰弱。得知此事的十七夜月 未來心疼不已，決心以自身妖力助他恢復元氣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >於是，在靜謐的深夜裡，一場只屬於兩人的療癒時光——〈妖狐的深夜特訓〉悄然展開。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/39f07ae3455f74507d2e81320c68637d.poster.avif?t=1776304865\" width=644 height=574 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/39f07ae3455f74507d2e81320c68637d.webm?t=1776304865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/39f07ae3455f74507d2e81320c68637d.mp4?t=1776304865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【高自由度的Live2D】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲主線內容使用Live2D製作，妖狐的身體會隨著玩家的操作產生即時反應。觸碰妖狐柔軟的肌膚，點燃她的情慾之火。本次針對新的場景追加了新的台詞及配音，提供更生動的視聽演出，讓妖狐發出欲罷不能的喘息聲吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/c44e78db1ec7ad54207fa33201e455e2.poster.avif?t=1776304865\" width=644 height=574 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/c44e78db1ec7ad54207fa33201e455e2.webm?t=1776304865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/c44e78db1ec7ad54207fa33201e455e2.mp4?t=1776304865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【特訓關卡】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每個特訓關卡都有不同的體位，縱享M字開腿、背後位、側躺等姿勢，讓你體驗征服傳說妖狐的快感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/41d55aaa16a042d5fc306809a0e8ca55.poster.avif?t=1776304865\" width=644 height=770 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/41d55aaa16a042d5fc306809a0e8ca55.webm?t=1776304865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/41d55aaa16a042d5fc306809a0e8ca55.mp4?t=1776304865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【工具解鎖】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當你完成與妖狐的特訓目標，將解鎖各種不同的工具，玩家可使用手、舌頭、肉棒和其他道具與妖狐進行深入交流，透過不同的工具，讓她逐漸沉迷於你高超的技巧無法自拔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/b6960732d91a8fd18cfbcc