c4d3ad140a84615f48b7cf2859/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1776304865", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/458843ec437327c4d3ad140a84615f48b7cf2859/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1776304865", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10 64bit OS<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i7-8700<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> Nvidia GeForce RTX 3050 or above</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10 64bits OS<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i7-8700<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> Nvidia GeForce RTX 3050 or above</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "developers": ["Fox House"], "publishers": ["Mango Party", "Mango Party News"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 15900, "final": 14300, "discount_percent": 10, "initial_formatted": "NT$ 159", "final_formatted": "NT$ 143"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "4", "description": "休閒"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2026 年 4 月 15 日"}}}}, "us": {"4257850": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Mirai's Midnight Training", "steam_appid": 4257850, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/64bf2e6607bc90659538384cc874d080.poster.avif?t=1776304865\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/64bf2e6607bc90659538384cc874d080.webm?t=1776304865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/64bf2e6607bc90659538384cc874d080.mp4?t=1776304865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Mirai's Midnight Training</strong></i><strong> is an after-story of <i>Mirai's Midnight Stream</i>.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Mirai's Midnight Training</strong></i><strong> is a standalone work. You do not need to own <i>Mirai's Midnight Stream</i> to play it, but we recommend playing <i>Mirai's Midnight Stream</i> for a better experience.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the days and nights passed, the exorcist gradually began to see how pure and gentle she actually was. The fox spirit was nothing like the evil being that people had described. The feelings between them quietly bloomed, and together they faced whatever challenges came their way. Let's also not forget how they saved the world from absolute destruction and defeated a divine beast sworn to slay the fox spirit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nevertheless, after traversing countless timelines and finally reaching the perfect ending, it was inevitable that the exorcist's body and spirit would weaken as his vital energy was depleted. Kanou Mirai was heartbroken, and resolved to use her yokai powers to help restore his vigor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shhh... It's midnight, and this healing session is just for these two. Who's ready for <i>Mirai's Midnight Training</i>?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/39f07ae3455f74507d2e81320c68637d.poster.avif?t=1776304865\" width=644 height=574 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/39f07ae3455f74507d2e81320c68637d.webm?t=1776304865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/39f07ae3455f74507d2e81320c68637d.mp4?t=1776304865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Super Free Live2D]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game's main story was produced using Live2D, so the fox spirit's body reacts instantly to the player's actions. Go on, touch her soft skin and ignite those naughty desires! New dialogue and voice acting have been added for the new scenes, offering a fresh, vivid audiovisual experience. C'mon, make that foxy fox moan!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/c44e78db1ec7ad54207fa33201e455e2.poster.avif?t=1776304865\" width=644 height=574 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/c44e78db1ec7ad54207fa33201e455e2.webm?t=1776304865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/c44e78db1ec7ad54207fa33201e455e2.mp4?t=1776304865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Training Stages]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each training stage features a different position. Enjoy positions such as the M-Squat, Doggy, Side Sex, and more. Conquer the legendary fox spirit  a new slew of positions!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/41d55aaa16a042d5fc306809a0e8ca55.poster.avif?t=1776304865\" width=644 height=770 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4257850/extras/41d55aaa16a042d5fc306809a0e8ca55.webm?t=1776304865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"